				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thank you so much ! This is the most useful and easy-to-use web font generator i&#8217;ve seen so far. After spending days looking for solutions to my problems (subsetting, hinting, font smoothing&#8230;), you finally provide (gracefully) a one-shot solution. The other guy is right, you are a  lifesaver ! </p>
